---
import Section from "@components/v1/section/Section.astro"
import PsyLogs from "./PsyLogs.astro"
import PsyDiv from "./PsyDiv.astro"
---

<Section id="section-psychology" class="section-psychology">
	<div class="section-psychology-heading">
		<h2 class="text-serif">Motivation</h2>
		<p>
			A 2-week personal log examining what actually drives my behavior
			most of the time, and what Self-Determination Theory says about it.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="section-psychology-content">
		<PsyDiv
			label="From April 10 to April 26"
			desc="Each entry records what I did and the tag reflects which motivation type I felt was driving it at that moment.">
			<PsyLogs />
		</PsyDiv>

		<PsyDiv
			label="Self-Determination Theory"
			desc=`"The term self-determination refers to a person\'s own ability to manage themselves, to make confident chouses, and to think on their own."`>
			<p class="sdt-pblock">
				Psychologists Edward Deci and Richard Ryan proposed that
				motivation isn't just "on or off" but fueled by three core
				psychological needs. When these needs are met, intrinsic
				motivation naturally grows. When they're blocked, we fall back
				on extrinsic drivers just to keep going.
			</p>
		</PsyDiv>
	</div>
</Section>

<style lang="scss">
	@use "@styles/modules/layouts";

	.section-psychology-heading,
	.section-psychology-content {
		@extend %grid-content;
	}

	.sdt-pblock {
		border-inline-start: 0.3em solid darkorange;
		border-top-right-radius: var(--global-border-radius);
		border-bottom-right-radius: var(--global-border-radius);
		background-color: var(--global-app-background-color-light1);

		padding: 1em 1.2em;
	}
</style>
